{
  "total_duration": 745.187,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 9.464,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Quick work"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“破案‘神速’”。先说答案：这个标题是 irony，反讽。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 9.814,
      "end": 22.909,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "正常的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "quick work"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是做事很快。但课文里，警察找回的是 Dan 二十年前丢的自行车，所以这个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "quick"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "听起来就很幽默。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 23.259,
      "end": 31.235,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Dan Robinson 收到当地警察局来信，第一反应不是开心，而是紧张："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Why do the police want me?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 31.585,
      "end": 41.145,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这很像今天突然收到学校办公室、派出所、物业、App 或短信通知：你还不知道原因，脑子已经开始自己编故事。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 41.495,
      "end": 51.823,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但这课不是 serious crime drama。Dan 没做错事，警察也不是吓人的。关键人物是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a smiling policeman"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，他带来的是好消息。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 52.173,
      "end": 68.012,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有一句要提前拆开："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "call at the station"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "call at"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是打电话，而是去某个地方一趟；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "station"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里是 police station，警察局，不是 train station。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 68.362,
      "end": 78.97,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文中文里有一句容易误会。意思不是“结果他一再担心了”，而是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "now he is not worried anymore"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，现在他不再担心了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 79.32,
      "end": 92.92,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天记忆链很短：letter -> police station -> worry -> smiling policeman -> bicycle found -> four hundred miles away -> by train -> surprised and amused -> stolen twenty years ago。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 93.27,
      "end": 99.582,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，从一封信开始："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dan Robinson has been worried all week."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 99.931,
      "end": 106.011,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么 worried？因为"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last Tuesday he received a letter from the local police."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 106.361,
      "end": 115.841,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "local police"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是他自己所在地区的警察。收到这种 official letter，人很容易紧张，因为原因还没说清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 116.191,
      "end": 120.515,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In the letter he was asked to call at the station."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 120.865,
      "end": 130.968,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "注意"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was asked"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是被动：Dan 收到要求。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "call at the station"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 go to the police station，去警察局一趟。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 131.318,
      "end": 138.438,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这幅画里，Dan 在家拿着警察局来信，脸上有 worry bubble：Why do the police want me?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 138.788,
      "end": 145.3,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，是 Dan 的担心和转折："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dan wondered why he was wanted by the police."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 145.65,
      "end": 154.482,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was wanted by the police"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "听起来很严重，所以 Dan 才会 nervous。但这里是 Dan 的想象，不是事实。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 154.832,
      "end": 160.824,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他还是去了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "but he went to the station yesterday and now he is not worried anymore."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 161.174,
      "end": 172.565,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "station"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还是 police station。后面出现"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "by train"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，那是运自行车的方式，不要把两个 station 混在一起。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 172.915,
      "end": 181.115,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到了警察局，画风变轻："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "At the station, he was told by a smiling policeman that his bicycle had been found."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 181.465,
      "end": 192.049,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "smiling policeman"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是信号：不是坏消息，是 found-item news，失物找回的消息。Dan 的 worry 开始变成 relief。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 192.399,
      "end": 203.927,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，神奇的不是破案快，而是距离远："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Five days ago, the policeman told him, the bicycle was picked up in a small village four hundred miles away."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 204.276,
      "end": 211.668,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was picked up"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是被人发现并收起来，finder 不重要，重要的是 bicycle was found。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 212.018,
      "end": 221.874,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "four hundred miles away"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很远。可以想象一辆旧自行车离开 Dan 的生活很久，突然从很远的小村庄冒出来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 222.224,
      "end": 226.904,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It is now being sent to his home by train."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 227.254,
      "end": 239.734,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "is being sent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示现在正在被送回去。这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "by train"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 transportation，用火车运，不是说 Dan 去了 train station。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 240.083,
      "end": 250.803,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这幅画要有轻松的荒诞感：old blue bicycle, small village, long distance, train return。好像一件童年物品自己旅行了二十年。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 251.153,
      "end": 257.413,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画，笑点落地："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dan was most surprised when he heard the news."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 257.763,
      "end": 267.967,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "most"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“世界上最惊讶的人”，而是 very，extremely。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "most surprised"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是非常惊讶。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 268.317,
      "end": 274.829,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "下一句更重要："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He was amused too, because he never expected the bicycle to be found."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 275.178,
      "end": 283.65,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "amused"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是觉得好笑，觉得这事有点离奇、有点有趣。Dan 不是害怕，也不是生气。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 284.0,
      "end": 291.016,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一句揭开标题反讽："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was stolen twenty years ago when Dan was a boy of fifteen!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 291.366,
      "end": 303.042,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "原来这不是“警察几天就破案”，而是“二十年前的自行车终于回来了”。所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Quick work"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "quick"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "才好笑。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 303.392,
      "end": 305.712,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我们来把这个故事的笑点说清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 306.061,
      "end": 310.385,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Quick work"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是说警察真的很快吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 310.735,
      "end": 321.967,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "字面上是 very fast work。但故事里，自行车是 twenty years ago 被偷的，所以说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "quick"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "反而是在开玩笑。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 322.317,
      "end": 324.908,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Dan 为什么担心一个星期？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 325.258,
      "end": 334.058,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为他只知道 local police 写信让他去 station，却不知道原因。Unknown official message makes people nervous。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 334.408,
      "end": 338.1,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "call at the station"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是打电话吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 338.45,
      "end": 348.493,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "call at"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里是 visit，go to a place。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "station"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里是 police station，警察局。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 348.843,
      "end": 351.694,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可后面又有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "by train"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 352.044,
      "end": 359.564,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，但那只是 bicycle is being sent by train，运送方式。课文没有说 Dan 去火车站。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 359.914,
      "end": 364.649,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "most surprised"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我能不能理解成“最惊讶”？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 364.999,
      "end": 373.319,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课里更自然的意思是 very surprised。它有一点正式、老派，跟这篇文章的幽默感很搭。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 373.669,
      "end": 383.709,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "背诵时抓住情绪变化：worried all week, nervous at the station, relieved by the smiling policeman, surprised and amused by the twenty-year-old bicycle."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 384.059,
      "end": 387.107,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dan Robinson has been worried all week."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 387.457,
      "end": 391.345,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last Tuesday he received a letter from the local police."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 391.695,
      "end": 395.103,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In the letter he was asked to call at the station."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 395.453,
      "end": 402.149,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dan wondered why he was wanted by the police, but he went to the station yesterday and now he is not worried anymore."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 402.499,
      "end": 407.779,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "At the station, he was told by a smiling policeman that his bicycle had been found."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 408.128,
      "end": 414.704,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Five days ago, the policeman told him, the bicycle was picked up in a small village four hundred miles away."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 415.054,
      "end": 418.198,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It is now being sent to his home by train."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 418.548,
      "end": 421.908,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dan was most surprised when he heard the news."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 422.258,
      "end": 427.034,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He was amused too, because he never expected the bicycle to be found."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 427.384,
      "end": 431.944,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was stolen twenty years ago when Dan was a boy of fifteen!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
