      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "amused"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 65,
      "start": 504.581,
      "end": 506.261,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "amused"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "amused"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 66,
      "start": 506.611,
      "end": 513.443,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "amused"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "amused"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是觉得好笑、觉得有趣，不是大笑到停不下来，也不是 mock someone。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 67,
      "start": 513.793,
      "end": 522.913,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "amused"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Dan was amused because the whole situation is strange and funny: he worried about the police, but the police had found his old bicycle."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 68,
      "start": 523.263,
      "end": 532.955,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "amused"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He was amused too, because he never expected the bicycle to be found."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话把 surprise 和 humor 连在一起。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 69,
      "start": 533.304,
      "end": 548.008,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "amused"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "三个词连起来看：Dan went to the"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "station"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ", was"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "most"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "surprised, and felt"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "amused"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "when the old bicycle came back."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 70,
      "start": 548.358,
      "end": 555.518,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 是 passive voice，被动语态。不要只背公式，要看故事为什么需要被动。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 71,
      "start": 555.868,
      "end": 561.348,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个故事关心的不是每个动作是谁做的，而是 Dan 和 bicycle 发生了什么。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 72,
      "start": 561.698,
      "end": 575.961,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一组是 Dan："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he was asked"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，信要求他去；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he was wanted by the police"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，这是 Dan 担心的想法；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he was told by a smiling policeman"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，警察告诉他好消息。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 73,
      "start": 576.311,
      "end": 591.742,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二组是 bicycle："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "his bicycle had been found"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，在 Dan 到之前已经被找到；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the bicycle was picked up"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，有人发现并收起它；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It is now being sent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，现在正在被送回家。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 74,
      "start": 592.092,
      "end": 601.412,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一击是过去："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was stolen twenty years ago"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。谁偷的不重要，重要的是这辆车二十年前就离开了 Dan。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 75,
      "start": 601.762,
      "end": 615.362,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以被动语态像一个 found-item report：Dan was asked, Dan was told, the bicycle had been found, the bicycle was picked up, it is being sent, and it was stolen long ago."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 76,
      "start": 615.712,
      "end": 629.239,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再看时间线："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "all week"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ","
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last Tuesday"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ","
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "yesterday"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ","
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Five days ago"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ","
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "now"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": ","
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "twenty years ago"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 77,
      "start": 629.589,
      "end": 637.389,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这些时间词让反转更清楚：Dan 担心的是 this week，但真正的故事从 twenty years ago 就开始了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 78,
      "start": 637.739,
      "end": 645.779,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "现在把这课放进自己的生活里。你收到学校办公室的信息，让你过去一趟。你不知道原因，所以有点担心。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 79,
      "start": 646.129,
      "end": 653.089,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到了以后，老师微笑着告诉你：你很久以前丢的 bicycle or schoolbag 被找到了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 80,
      "start": 653.439,
      "end": 660.719,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你要练三件事：say you received a message, explain the item was found, and describe your feeling."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 81,
      "start": 661.069,
      "end": 665.453,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以这样开头："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I received a message from the school office."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 82,
      "start": 665.803,
      "end": 670.259,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后用被动："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I was asked to go there, so I was worried."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 83,
      "start": 670.608,
      "end": 675.248,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再说好消息："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I was told that my bicycle had been found."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 84,
      "start": 675.598,
      "end": 682.142,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后点出感受："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I was very surprised and amused, because I never expected it to be found."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 85,
      "start": 682.492,
      "end": 692.372,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这题的重点是让 passive voice 有用：不是只会做语法题，而是能讲 lost item, found item, unexpected good news。"
        }
      ]
    },
